* [[Football League Two Manager of the Month]]: September 2010 & November 2010

;Promotions
* [[1996<U+2013>97 in English football|1996<U+2013>97]]: [[Football League Third Division|Third Division]] Runner Up (promotion to the [[Football League Second Division|Second Division]]) <U+2013> [[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]]
* [[2000<U+2013>01 in English football|2000<U+2013>01]]: [[Football League Third Division|Third Division]] Champion (promotion to the [[Football League Second Division|Second Division]]) <U+2013> [[Brighton & Hove Albion F.C.|Brighton & Hove Albion]]
* [[2002<U+2013>03 in English football|2002<U+2013>03]]: [[Football League First Division|First Division]] Runner Up (promotion to the [[Premier League]]) <U+2013> [[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]]

;Trophies
;[[Port Vale F.C.|Port Vale]]
* [[Staffordshire Senior Cup]] runners-up: 2010

